{"tid":1686985,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】維園集會遭警反對 逾百民主派候選人11.2改辦選舉聚會","createTime":"2019-11-01T13:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T13:42:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22904828de0a082d5ee9a0ff1962a247e9fe40a0","tid":1686985,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:33:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191101/60217719?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191101%2F60217719%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvFuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=18c7fd71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191101%2F60217719%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&h=d881730f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191101/60217719?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】維園集會遭警反對 逾百民主派候選人11.2改辦選舉聚會<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191031/large/1572533973_2487.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191031%2Flarge%2F1572533973_2487.jpg&h=1cbd9333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為往年7.1維園集會。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n曾為多個「反送中」遊行和集會申請警方「不反對通知書」的劉頴匡，日前再申請本周六（2日）在維園集會，卻遭警方反對。百多名民主派區議會選舉候選人宣佈，積極考慮按《選舉條例》第12（5）條，於本周六下午3時在維多利亞公園中央草坪舉行選舉聚會。各候選人等將在草坪不同位置各自進行選舉聚會，預計每個聚會有不多於50名支持者出席，毋須通知警方。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【抗暴之戰】疑中警催淚彈 72歲婆婆左腳血流如注<br />\n<br />\n面對警方剝奪市民遊行集會權利，全港18區共100多名民主派候選人，包括東區徐子見、南區袁嘉蔚、荃灣岑敖暉、屯門巫堃泰等發表聯合聲明，宣佈積極考慮根據《選舉條例》第12（5）條，於本周六下午3時正在維多利亞公園中央草坪發起選舉聚會。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，各候選人會在草坪的不同位置各自進行選舉聚會，每個聚會歡迎不多於50名支持者出席，毋須通知警方。而各名候選人屆時會重申捍衞港人自由的立場，並呼籲選民在選舉中支持民主派候選人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【抗暴之戰】廢中之意不在酒 &mdash; 梁栢堅<br />\n<br />\n對於警方早前就劉頴匡在同一時間和地點的集會發出禁止集會通知書，百多名民主派候選人在聲明中表示，強烈譴責警方打壓市民在《基本法》下的集會自由。他們重申，守護香港人的言論和集會自由，是民主派候選人的共同理念。<br />\n<br />\n其他候選人資料可瀏覽 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MUQywa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MUQywa&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvFuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=046816b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MUQywa</a><br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n2019區選專頁<br />\n光復香港 11.24踢走共產黨<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【撐學生】<br />\n召集有心人 撐學生全年睇《蘋果》<br />\n立即按此<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n百日特刊記載香港人逆權之路<br />\n《逆權百日》<br />\n《自由之夏》<br />\n《Freedom Summer》（自由之夏英文版） <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【短片】【抗暴之戰】廢中之意不在酒 &mdash; 梁栢堅<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【短片】【區選光復香港●北區】建制派「引清兵」入城 拒減自由行縱容水貨黨"},{"pid":"b10b2c31eedd66ba39ebead9f64405a79cf923c0","tid":1686985,"uid":130678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},{"pid":"65692b79ad91d05f87e3df270d81c709b253ae78","tid":1686985,"uid":130678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b10b2c31eedd66ba39ebead9f64405a79cf923c0","tid":1686985,"uid":130678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a88e631a882ceaad3f05805362dd879e845f7f","tid":1686985,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}